data.description:
Pool, Boat dock, trails, lake and so much more in these neighborhood amenities! Located in a cul-de-sac, away from busy streets, traffic, and inside of the desired Marine Creek Ranch, you'll find your new home! This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom, offers 2,334 sqft of comfortable and open, living space with all of the natural lighting you could ask for. A fireplace in the living area, a bonus living area on the second floor, walk in closets, and private backyard with mature trees, makes this a perfect home for entertaining with plenty of shade, during the Texas summer!

This home is well-cared-for and ready for you to move right in! Don’t miss your chance, schedule a showing today!
